WEBVTT

01:37.860 --> 01:41.000
[The Epoch of Miyu]

01:41.080 --> 01:43.960
[Episode 22]

01:46.150 --> 01:47.479
Just to do Bai Yongjun a favor.

01:47.479 --> 01:49.880
After all, he highly recommended that guy.

01:52.640 --> 01:54.170
Do you have someone in mind?

01:58.310 --> 01:59.120
Look at this.

02:00.920 --> 02:04.030
[Career Direction Assessment Report]

02:01.430 --> 02:04.490
This person's assessment result
is quite impressive.

02:04.510 --> 02:06.280
Born to work in the hotel industry.

02:06.280 --> 02:07.540
A bright future ahead.

02:08.150 --> 02:08.960
Who is this?

02:10.150 --> 02:10.910
Xu Miyu.

02:13.870 --> 02:16.560
This kind of assessment
is similar to MBTI.

02:16.560 --> 02:17.310
It's just for reference.

02:17.310 --> 02:18.710
We shouldn't blindly trust it.

02:18.710 --> 02:19.870
Besides, you should know

02:19.870 --> 02:22.840
that cross-department transformation is
troublesome.

02:22.840 --> 02:24.870
I can handle complicated procedures.

02:24.870 --> 02:26.400
Now, what I'm not sure about is

02:26.400 --> 02:28.530
whether my decision is too arbitrary.

02:28.960 --> 02:30.190
What do you think, Rui?

02:30.190 --> 02:32.000
Is Xu Miyu really capable of

02:32.190 --> 02:34.190
being our lobby manager?

02:36.730 --> 02:39.160
I saw her performance earlier today.

02:38.840 --> 02:41.100
[Purong Hotel]

02:39.310 --> 02:42.310
She is as calm and resourceful as Anna.

02:42.310 --> 02:44.710
And she knows the hotel's situation
very well.

02:44.710 --> 02:46.400
She is a very good candidate.

02:46.520 --> 02:47.590
However,

02:51.120 --> 02:53.280
I don't know Xu Miyu's opinion.

02:53.560 --> 02:55.030
How about I talk to her?

02:55.970 --> 02:56.500
Okay.

03:10.000 --> 03:11.360
Transfer me to the Front Office?

03:11.360 --> 03:12.160
That's right.

03:13.240 --> 03:15.300
This is our preliminary resolution.

03:15.430 --> 03:18.240
It still needs to go through
a management vote.

03:18.520 --> 03:20.430
Also, we need to consider
your personal wishes.

03:20.430 --> 03:22.590
So, I came to talk to you first today.

03:23.150 --> 03:24.210
Are you willing to?

03:28.000 --> 03:28.630
Thank you.

03:35.520 --> 03:36.320
Director Bai.

03:36.710 --> 03:38.630
Ms. An started her maternity leave
ahead of schedule yesterday.

03:38.630 --> 03:40.160
You know about this, right?

03:40.520 --> 03:42.280
So, now, in the Front Office,

03:42.280 --> 03:44.480
a lobby manager position has opened up.

03:45.590 --> 03:47.520
The leaders attach great importance
to this matter.

03:47.520 --> 03:49.590
After discussing it with
the HR Department,

03:49.590 --> 03:52.190
they've decided to assign
a new lobby manager.

03:53.590 --> 03:55.650
Why do they need to send someone over?

03:55.710 --> 03:56.310
Who is it?

03:57.000 --> 03:58.800
Has the candidate been decided?

03:59.000 --> 04:00.430
It hasn't been finalized yet.

04:00.430 --> 04:02.750
It's just a pending candidate.

04:06.590 --> 04:07.740
I want to know

04:09.150 --> 04:10.280
why you chose me.

04:10.710 --> 04:12.170
Do you remember this test?

04:13.140 --> 04:15.410
[Controlling][Influential][Strict][Calm]

04:14.280 --> 04:15.750
According to the report,

04:16.120 --> 04:17.190
in the aspects of image,

04:17.190 --> 04:19.250
communication skills, and loyalty,

04:19.680 --> 04:21.269
you are stronger than

04:21.269 --> 04:22.870
other candidates

04:22.870 --> 04:24.130
for the lobby manager.

04:24.830 --> 04:25.830
What do you think?

04:29.870 --> 04:31.270
Do you have any concerns?

04:33.480 --> 04:34.870
I have a concern.

04:35.750 --> 04:38.120
Is it because you are my friends

04:38.750 --> 04:40.480
and you are overestimating me?

04:40.590 --> 04:41.570
Mr. Xue,

04:42.360 --> 04:43.690
to be honest, recently,

04:43.800 --> 04:45.830
I indeed felt a bit confused about

04:45.830 --> 04:47.190
my career planning.

04:47.409 --> 04:49.490
That is why I took this evaluation.

04:50.280 --> 04:51.960
If I say I don't want to get promoted,

04:51.960 --> 04:53.190
it will be a lie.

04:53.240 --> 04:54.510
Today, knowing that

04:54.510 --> 04:56.110
I have so many possibilities,

04:56.110 --> 04:58.280
and could even become a lobby manager,

04:58.800 --> 05:00.120
I am truly happy.

05:00.560 --> 05:02.750
I also wish I could tell you

05:02.750 --> 05:04.020
that I'm willing to give it a try.

05:04.020 --> 05:05.220
However,

05:05.270 --> 05:07.310
this is a cross-departmental promotion
after all.

05:07.310 --> 05:09.610
Besides, I'm far from familiar with

05:09.630 --> 05:11.510
the front desk work.

05:12.360 --> 05:13.480
I think

05:13.480 --> 05:15.210
you trust me unconditionally,

05:15.270 --> 05:17.120
because you guys are my friends.

05:17.120 --> 05:19.130
But also, for that reason,

05:19.160 --> 05:20.600
I'm even more afraid of

05:21.510 --> 05:22.630
letting you down.

05:23.480 --> 05:25.040
Forewoman of the executive floor?

05:25.040 --> 05:27.600
Xu Miyu, the one
who always flatters the leader?

05:27.600 --> 05:29.460
Director Bai, you freaked me out.

05:29.560 --> 05:30.920
Subordinates are spreading rumors.

05:30.920 --> 05:32.780
But we shouldn't join in the fuss.

05:33.830 --> 05:35.240
Ms. Xu is exceptionally capable

05:35.240 --> 05:36.560
in her work.

05:36.680 --> 05:39.320
In the opening of the Chinese restaurant

05:39.430 --> 05:41.750
and Ms. An's emergency yesterday,

05:41.750 --> 05:43.040
she was at the front line

05:43.040 --> 05:44.600
and did an excellent job.

05:44.630 --> 05:46.310
It's obvious to everyone.

05:55.180 --> 05:57.070
Did the HSKP Department kick her out

05:57.070 --> 05:59.070
and shove her into the Front Office?

05:59.310 --> 06:01.000
She's just a forewoman.

06:01.000 --> 06:03.000
How could she be a lobby manager?

06:03.870 --> 06:05.680
When promoting someone,

06:05.680 --> 06:07.950
we need to emphasize person-job fit.

06:08.310 --> 06:09.630
Not to mention that the lobby manager,

06:09.630 --> 06:11.160
who is the face of our hotel.

06:11.270 --> 06:12.430
It connects upwards to
the general manager

06:12.430 --> 06:15.290
and downwards to
every department and every guest.

06:15.750 --> 06:18.190
You guys found such an ass-kisser
to fool me?

06:18.190 --> 06:19.280
Your tricks are

06:19.430 --> 06:20.720
too blatant.

06:21.300 --> 06:22.100
Xu Miyu.

06:23.170 --> 06:24.490
I'm sitting here

06:24.800 --> 06:27.680
not to represent Mr. Ji and myself,

06:27.920 --> 06:30.050
but for the interests of Purong Hotel.

06:30.120 --> 06:32.040
Meanwhile, since we are friends,

06:32.040 --> 06:33.950
we will not put you

06:33.980 --> 06:35.320
in an unsuitable position,

06:35.320 --> 06:36.760
letting you bear

06:36.790 --> 06:38.520
undue pressure and criticism.

06:38.830 --> 06:40.480
Just as we believe in you,

06:40.840 --> 06:42.440
we hope you can believe in us,

06:42.720 --> 06:44.720
and more importantly, in yourself.

06:47.070 --> 06:48.390
I understand, Mr. Xue.

06:50.680 --> 06:52.120
May I ask

06:52.140 --> 06:53.500
who recommended me?

06:53.780 --> 06:55.440
Is the answer that important?

06:59.240 --> 07:00.440
It was Mr. Ji himself.

07:11.250 --> 07:12.560
If you really

07:12.560 --> 07:14.220
don't know where your path is,

07:14.360 --> 07:16.820
you might as well start with
trial and error.

07:16.940 --> 07:18.540
Step out of your comfort zone

07:18.670 --> 07:21.440
and see the other sides of that iceberg.

07:20.920 --> 07:23.750
♪ Bury everything in your mind ♪

07:21.620 --> 07:24.110
Meeting guests' needs
is your responsibility,

07:24.110 --> 07:25.790
while supporting you is mine.

07:24.920 --> 07:27.550
♪ Hope love blossoms as wished ♪

07:26.380 --> 07:28.140
I'm your boss.

07:28.420 --> 07:29.980
I will be responsible for you.

07:28.480 --> 07:31.940
♪ Rainwater silently nourishes flowers ♪

07:30.160 --> 07:31.820
You can trust me a little more,

07:31.930 --> 07:32.500
okay?

07:33.570 --> 07:34.550
♪ At its own expense ♪

07:34.960 --> 07:38.150
In the past,
when faced with things I wanted,

07:35.870 --> 07:38.590
♪ In the hot summer ♪

07:38.180 --> 07:39.480
I was always used to putting in

07:39.480 --> 07:41.560
a little more effort than others,

07:39.760 --> 07:42.670
♪ I'm melting ♪

07:42.230 --> 07:45.010
cautiously pleasing others and weighing

07:43.420 --> 07:48.750
♪ Before the flowers wither,
I pretend to be cool ♪

07:45.320 --> 07:47.650
just to prove that I deserved
to have them.

07:48.280 --> 07:51.650
But now he keeps telling me

07:50.370 --> 07:51.870
♪  Ah  ♪

07:52.510 --> 07:53.800
that everyone in this world

07:52.740 --> 07:55.950
♪Talking to myself♪

07:53.800 --> 07:55.800
is a shining star.

07:56.970 --> 07:59.810
I can be seen without trying to
please others.

07:57.440 --> 07:58.850
♪Ah♪

07:59.730 --> 08:04.080
♪ Though I'm alone,
I pretend to be at ease ♪

08:00.790 --> 08:04.190
I deserve to be firmly chosen
without having to prove myself.

08:05.180 --> 08:07.300
♪ That fleeting moment I tried to hold ♪

08:05.200 --> 08:06.720
[Chapter 2: Project Management Process]

08:06.830 --> 08:09.840
[Chapter 3: Project Activation]

08:08.210 --> 08:11.160
♪ Let it go when the glass runs dry ♪

08:08.320 --> 08:11.350
For you, moving from the HSKP Department
to the Front Office,

08:09.930 --> 08:11.020
[Project Selection and Feasibility Study]

08:11.870 --> 08:12.750
in terms of specific work content,

08:12.180 --> 08:15.100
♪ Unfinished longings ♪

08:12.750 --> 08:15.410
you will face new challenges
and difficulties.

08:15.530 --> 08:17.160
You need to get prepared.

08:15.840 --> 08:18.900
♪ Drift like fading embers ♪

08:17.680 --> 08:19.400
As for any other problems,

08:19.630 --> 08:20.870
don't worry.

08:20.090 --> 08:22.290
♪ Still longing for yesterday's glow ♪

08:20.590 --> 08:24.900
[Project Selection and Feasibility Study]

08:21.270 --> 08:22.730
Leave them to Mr. Ji and me.

08:22.930 --> 08:25.120
I will work hard not to let you down.

08:23.170 --> 08:25.980
♪ Yet sailing into
the ocean's depths at night ♪

08:26.480 --> 08:29.480
Xu Miyu, do you remember what I told you

08:27.010 --> 08:30.090
♪ Questions without answers ♪

08:29.480 --> 08:30.920
in your interview?

08:31.070 --> 08:33.720
♪ Let them go with the wind ♪

08:32.789 --> 08:34.360
Purong Hotel will provide everyone

08:34.360 --> 08:35.909
who has career aspirations

08:35.179 --> 08:36.720
♪ Let them go ♪

08:35.909 --> 08:38.390
with a matching path for promotion.

08:39.380 --> 08:41.770
So, you should believe in yourself.

08:41.820 --> 08:43.010
One day,

08:43.200 --> 08:46.260
you will definitely become
an excellent hotel worker.

09:09.280 --> 09:10.440
Your clothes have been washed.

09:10.440 --> 09:11.130
Thank you.

09:11.190 --> 09:12.480
Do you need anything else?

09:12.480 --> 09:13.240
No.

09:15.590 --> 09:17.380
Hello.
Here is the mineral water you asked for.

09:17.380 --> 09:17.940
Thank you.

09:17.940 --> 09:19.240
Do you need anything else?

09:19.240 --> 09:20.030
No.

09:46.270 --> 09:47.270
Room service.

09:47.480 --> 09:49.540
-Sorry, sir.
-Get it right next time.

09:51.610 --> 09:52.730
It's you.

10:07.960 --> 10:08.800
Miyu.

10:09.120 --> 10:10.000
No need, no need.

10:10.000 --> 10:11.930
I made the bed myself this morning.

10:13.120 --> 10:14.870
Then, I'll go outside.

10:21.200 --> 10:22.000
Listen, Miyu.

10:22.000 --> 10:23.240
The floor is perfectly clean.

10:23.240 --> 10:25.170
You don't need to clean it anymore.

10:25.270 --> 10:26.630
Can you please

10:26.630 --> 10:28.510
stop doing one chore after another?

10:28.510 --> 10:29.120
Come here.

10:29.120 --> 10:32.080
Sit down and chat with me.

10:32.080 --> 10:34.600
Daniel, I am your butler first,

10:34.600 --> 10:36.170
and then, your friend.

10:36.270 --> 10:38.470
Taking care of your daily life is my job.

10:38.500 --> 10:39.960
You have to let me finish my work first.

10:39.960 --> 10:40.600
No problem.

10:40.600 --> 10:42.200
Leave the work for tomorrow.

10:43.600 --> 10:46.600
It might not be me tomorrow.

10:47.870 --> 10:48.840
What?

10:50.920 --> 10:52.920
Is someone trying to fire you again?

10:53.020 --> 10:53.960
Tell me.

10:53.960 --> 10:55.290
I'll tell the Old Madam.

10:55.640 --> 10:57.760
Let's see who dares to bully you again.

10:57.760 --> 10:58.760
This is too much.

10:58.780 --> 11:01.060
You mean when I was about to be fired,

11:01.090 --> 11:03.090
Aunt Wanjun helped me?

11:07.000 --> 11:08.190
Chairman Wei.

11:10.120 --> 11:12.240
Why so distant?

11:12.260 --> 11:13.940
For what happened before,

11:14.910 --> 11:15.960
thank you.

11:16.440 --> 11:17.750
There's nothing to be embarrassed about.

11:17.750 --> 11:19.480
She is your chairwoman,

11:19.480 --> 11:21.000
your Aunt Wanjun,

11:21.000 --> 11:22.510
and also my cousin Wanjun.

11:22.510 --> 11:24.200
Who is your cousin?

11:24.220 --> 11:25.500
You old fool.

11:27.320 --> 11:27.870
By the way.

11:27.870 --> 11:30.070
Miyu, let's continue where we left off.

11:30.240 --> 11:32.580
Who wronged you again?

11:32.640 --> 11:34.370
You'd better tell us

11:34.400 --> 11:35.520
everything.

11:35.540 --> 11:37.510
Your chairwoman will stand up for you.

11:37.510 --> 11:38.320
Actually,

11:38.600 --> 11:40.390
I wasn't wronged,

11:40.390 --> 11:42.390
and I don't need anyone to
stand up for me.

11:42.390 --> 11:43.360
It's just that

11:44.220 --> 11:47.150
I'm going to be the lobby manager
at the Front Office.

11:48.010 --> 11:49.140
You got a promotion!

11:50.390 --> 11:51.910
That's great news.

11:52.240 --> 11:53.630
Why didn't you tell me just now?

11:53.630 --> 11:55.360
You made me worry for nothing.

11:55.360 --> 11:56.000
I'm sweating.

11:56.000 --> 11:57.240
I am happy.

11:58.600 --> 12:01.200
But I'm a little reluctant to leave.

12:06.490 --> 12:08.310
There's nothing to be reluctant about.

12:08.310 --> 12:09.340
Young people

12:09.370 --> 12:11.970
should stride forward.

12:12.000 --> 12:13.720
Don't overthink things.

12:13.720 --> 12:15.960
Do not act like an old madam.

12:16.120 --> 12:18.390
What do you mean?

12:18.390 --> 12:20.080
Can't you just keep quiet?

12:24.160 --> 12:24.960
Miyu.

12:25.480 --> 12:27.000
I heard

12:27.370 --> 12:28.260
that Mr. Ji

12:28.320 --> 12:30.000
was under immense pressure

12:30.020 --> 12:32.250
to recommend
a forewoman of the HSKP Department

12:32.250 --> 12:33.690
to be the lobby manager.

12:34.080 --> 12:36.120
I had a feeling it was you.

12:36.280 --> 12:37.640
Congratulations.

12:37.960 --> 12:40.360
Getting promoted under Mr. Ji

12:40.380 --> 12:42.770
fully proves your capability.

12:44.380 --> 12:45.780
Thank you, Chairman Wei.

12:46.280 --> 12:47.390
Aunt Wanjun.

12:48.120 --> 12:49.200
Thank you, Daniel.

12:49.480 --> 12:51.240
I'll leave it to you.

12:51.260 --> 12:52.220
I'll be leaving now.

12:52.220 --> 12:52.910
Okay.

13:53.010 --> 13:54.470
Are you still hesitating?

13:55.040 --> 13:56.280
Are you wondering

13:56.610 --> 13:58.090
"if I am truly qualified

13:58.110 --> 13:59.370
to be a lobby manager?"

14:00.320 --> 14:03.050
Or "what kind of pawn Ji Feng
is using me as?

14:03.080 --> 14:05.140
Will he push me into the crosshairs?"

14:08.210 --> 14:10.140
Purong Hotel doesn't belong to me.

14:10.570 --> 14:12.370
You must believe that it can provide

14:12.370 --> 14:14.480
every capable and ambitious person

14:14.820 --> 14:16.460
with a path to get promoted.

14:17.320 --> 14:18.290
Striving for higher ground

14:18.290 --> 14:19.550
is an eternal pursuit.

14:20.430 --> 14:22.830
If you don't move forward,
you fall behind.

14:22.940 --> 14:25.650
This time, I've decided to move forward.

14:26.240 --> 14:27.220
By the way, Mr. Ji,

14:27.220 --> 14:28.320
I heard that this opportunity

14:28.320 --> 14:30.360
was something you fought hard
to get for me.

14:30.360 --> 14:32.930
I want to sincerely thank you.

14:37.130 --> 14:39.690
What kind of place
do you think the lobby is?

14:42.790 --> 14:43.960
The lobby

14:44.440 --> 14:45.870
should be the first impression

14:45.870 --> 14:48.160
a hotel gives its guests.

14:48.550 --> 14:50.320
When I used to book hotels,

14:50.320 --> 14:52.220
I would also pay special attention
to the lobby.

14:52.220 --> 14:54.670
Even though I don't spend much time
in the lobby,

14:54.670 --> 14:57.260
a bright and spacious one

14:57.290 --> 14:59.620
really makes me want to
stay at that hotel.

15:00.870 --> 15:03.080
You and every staff member here

15:03.560 --> 15:05.760
are the first sight of Purong Hotel.

15:06.640 --> 15:08.170
A competent lobby manager

15:08.200 --> 15:10.400
must not only uphold the hotel's image,

15:10.530 --> 15:12.870
but also reflect its warmth,

15:13.110 --> 15:14.750
elegance, and attitude.

15:15.910 --> 15:18.190
The one guests seek help from the most
when they walk through this door

15:18.190 --> 15:19.400
is the lobby manager.

15:19.420 --> 15:20.600
It is no exaggeration to say that

15:20.600 --> 15:21.580
a lobby manager

15:21.700 --> 15:23.640
is the hotel's encyclopedia.

15:29.730 --> 15:30.800
Try to imagine that

15:31.250 --> 15:32.440
you are that door.

15:32.780 --> 15:33.930
Do not hold back those who left,

15:33.930 --> 15:35.660
and do not reject those who will come.

15:35.660 --> 15:37.770
When you become one with this space

15:38.500 --> 15:40.030
and can navigate it freely,

15:41.080 --> 15:42.520
you have truly embarked on

15:42.520 --> 15:43.850
your career path.

15:46.710 --> 15:47.970
Don't doubt yourself.

15:48.400 --> 15:49.800
Seize this opportunity.

16:00.710 --> 16:02.080
Letter of Appointment:

16:02.510 --> 16:04.550
Based on the hotel's operational
and developmental needs,

16:04.550 --> 16:06.270
after a management meeting,

16:06.270 --> 16:08.910
new personnel appointments have been made.

16:08.910 --> 16:10.870
The specific appointments are as follows:

16:10.870 --> 16:12.870
Xu Miyu is appointed to be

16:12.900 --> 16:14.790
the lobby manager of Front Office,
in responsible for

16:14.790 --> 16:18.000
the all-round management
and operation of the lobby

16:18.000 --> 16:20.840
as well as the coordination
and optimization of guest services.

16:20.840 --> 16:23.150
Luo Qingping is hereby appointed

16:23.150 --> 16:25.510
as the forewoman of
the HSKP Department's executive floor,

16:25.510 --> 16:26.790
responsible for the executive floor's

16:26.790 --> 16:28.950
daily management and operations

16:29.150 --> 16:31.720
as well as the coordination
and optimization of guest services

16:31.720 --> 16:33.790
to continuously improve

16:33.790 --> 16:37.320
service quality and operational efficiency
on the executive floor,

16:37.320 --> 16:40.150
and fully showcasing
the hotel's premium image.

16:40.390 --> 16:43.200
The above appointments are effective
immediately upon announcement.

16:43.200 --> 16:44.080
Hereby notified.

16:44.080 --> 16:46.080
Purong Hotel HR Department.

16:47.390 --> 16:48.150
Congratulations.

16:48.150 --> 16:48.910
Thank you.

16:50.550 --> 16:51.320
Congratulations.

16:51.320 --> 16:51.910
Thank you.

16:51.910 --> 16:53.080
Change your clothes later.

16:53.080 --> 16:54.790
I'll take you to meet your new colleagues.

16:54.790 --> 16:55.670
Right now?

16:55.670 --> 16:56.790
It's required for work.

16:56.790 --> 16:58.030
I'll wait for you in the lobby
on the first floor.

16:58.030 --> 16:58.870
Okay.

16:59.750 --> 17:02.080
-Miyu, I don’t want you to leave.
-Miyu.

17:02.320 --> 17:04.680
Miyu, are you just going to
leave us behind?

17:04.680 --> 17:05.930
I will miss you.

17:06.200 --> 17:08.060
I don't want to leave you, either.

17:08.069 --> 17:09.400
But I'm not really leaving.

17:09.400 --> 17:10.750
I'm just in the lobby.

17:10.920 --> 17:12.310
If you miss me,

17:12.310 --> 17:13.200
come find me,

17:13.200 --> 17:14.730
or send me a WeChat message.

17:16.160 --> 17:17.680
Time to work.

17:18.829 --> 17:19.550
Go ahead.

17:27.030 --> 17:27.810
Qingping.

17:28.550 --> 17:29.550
From now on,

17:29.790 --> 17:31.390
these brothers and sisters,

17:31.830 --> 17:33.830
as well as our guests
on the executive floor,

17:33.830 --> 17:34.830
are in your hands.

17:35.720 --> 17:36.590
Don't worry.

17:37.160 --> 17:39.680
I will do even better than you.

17:42.790 --> 17:43.550
Thank you.

17:55.630 --> 17:59.830
[HSKP Department, Xu Miyu]

18:01.780 --> 18:03.250
[HSKP Department, Xu Miyu]

18:05.830 --> 18:07.000
Since today,

18:07.000 --> 18:10.000
Xu Miyu will be the forewoman of
the executive floor.

18:10.720 --> 18:12.400
When Black Card Ji
cancelled your bad reviews,

18:12.400 --> 18:13.400
I could sense it.

18:13.400 --> 18:15.060
You have a strong background.

18:15.590 --> 18:16.590
Allergic to the towel?

18:16.590 --> 18:17.920
Just in the past few days,

18:17.920 --> 18:19.750
I kept sleeping
with the towel under my neck

18:19.750 --> 18:22.440
and got an allergic reaction.

18:23.000 --> 18:24.530
Who are you trying to scare?

18:24.750 --> 18:26.440
Aren't you just a forewoman?

18:26.960 --> 18:28.780
You're just a floor forewoman.

18:29.000 --> 18:31.550
How dare you talk to me
about a common position?

18:31.550 --> 18:33.000
Who do you think you are?

18:36.240 --> 18:37.200
Found it.

18:38.830 --> 18:40.590
Miyu, I'm sorry.

18:40.610 --> 18:42.480
I won't disclose this matter.

18:42.920 --> 18:44.090
But I have to remind you that

18:44.090 --> 18:45.160
you should never

18:45.160 --> 18:46.240
make such a mistake again.

18:46.240 --> 18:47.240
Thank you, Miyu.

18:47.240 --> 18:48.670
You are such an angel. Thank you.

18:48.670 --> 18:50.720
I'll have this girl tally up

18:50.720 --> 18:52.720
who wants to share the Yan Du Xian.

18:52.720 --> 18:53.590
Does that work for you?

18:53.590 --> 18:54.830
The manager always has a way.

18:54.830 --> 18:56.720
You are the most considerate
hotel attendant

18:56.720 --> 18:59.510
I've ever met.

18:59.750 --> 19:01.150
Penalties must be given,

19:01.260 --> 19:03.160
but compensations must also be made.

19:03.160 --> 19:04.160
Let's get to work.

19:38.270 --> 19:40.270
Chairman Wei, what brings you here?

19:41.070 --> 19:41.920
Today is

19:41.920 --> 19:44.590
your first day as a lobby manager.

19:44.680 --> 19:46.240
I came to cheer you on.

19:46.240 --> 19:47.200
Good luck.

19:48.000 --> 19:48.720
Thank you.

19:50.040 --> 19:50.840
Look.

19:53.680 --> 19:56.950
On my first day working at Purong,

19:57.090 --> 19:58.610
my mother gave this to me.

19:59.160 --> 20:00.030
Today,

20:00.720 --> 20:01.960
I am giving it to you.

20:04.210 --> 20:07.200
I hope every day you work at Purong,

20:07.320 --> 20:08.710
it stays with you.

20:08.100 --> 20:09.280
[Purong Hotel, Front Office, Xu Miyu]

20:09.880 --> 20:11.210
How can I accept this?

20:11.240 --> 20:12.570
It suits you perfectly.

20:13.960 --> 20:16.160
Ms. Xu, are you in the lobby?

20:16.660 --> 20:17.820
Yes.

20:18.110 --> 20:19.070
Go on.

20:19.090 --> 20:20.820
I'll watch you leave from here.

20:33.730 --> 20:34.410
Here she is.

20:35.240 --> 20:36.480
Everyone is here.

20:36.850 --> 20:38.330
Great. Please announce.

20:42.070 --> 20:43.400
Letter of Appointment:

20:43.830 --> 20:46.310
Based on the hotel's operational
and developmental needs,

20:46.310 --> 20:48.380
after a management meeting,

20:48.550 --> 20:51.590
a new personnel appointment has been made.

20:51.790 --> 20:53.320
The details are as follows:

20:53.510 --> 20:55.440
Xu Miyu is appointed to be

20:55.440 --> 20:57.510
the lobby manager of Front Office,
in responsible for

20:57.510 --> 21:01.320
the all-round management and operation of
the lobby of the Front Office,

21:01.320 --> 21:04.380
and the coordination
and optimization of guest services

21:04.380 --> 21:06.240
to continuously improve

21:06.240 --> 21:09.160
the lobby service quality and
the operational efficiency

21:09.160 --> 21:12.270
and present the hotel's excellent image.

21:12.440 --> 21:15.400
The above appointment will take effect
from the date of publication.

21:15.400 --> 21:16.400
This is to notify.

21:16.790 --> 21:18.510
Purong Hotel HR Department.

21:19.430 --> 21:19.980
Congratulations.

21:19.980 --> 21:20.670
Thank you.

21:21.790 --> 21:24.070
Now, let's welcome our new lobby manager,

21:24.070 --> 21:26.070
Xu Miyu, to say a few words.

21:36.750 --> 21:38.350
Hello everyone, I'm Xu Miyu.

21:38.750 --> 21:42.480
It's a great honor to
join the Front Office team

21:42.480 --> 21:44.000
and become one of you.

21:45.240 --> 21:47.240
I hope from now on we can work

21:47.510 --> 21:48.590
side by side.

21:48.750 --> 21:51.480
I also hope to do a good job in service.

21:51.890 --> 21:52.850
More importantly,

21:52.850 --> 21:55.720
I hope to get everyone's support and help.

21:57.000 --> 21:57.920
Thank you all.

22:05.330 --> 22:06.520
Good!

22:06.550 --> 22:07.640
Awesome!

22:07.840 --> 22:08.900
Applause, please.

22:10.050 --> 22:11.980
Let's give her a round of applause.

22:13.000 --> 22:13.720
Ms. Xu.

22:14.200 --> 22:16.440
Welcome to the Front Office.

22:16.750 --> 22:18.400
You are so beautiful and capable.

22:18.400 --> 22:19.550
Being a forewoman in the HSKP Department

22:19.550 --> 22:21.960
was indeed a waste of your talents.

22:22.030 --> 22:23.070
Now that you are in our Front Office,

22:23.070 --> 22:25.590
we will give you a stage
to fully showcase your abilities.

22:25.590 --> 22:27.550
I believe you will bring
new breakthroughs to the lobby's work

22:27.550 --> 22:28.750
and create new achievements

22:28.750 --> 22:30.120
in the future.

22:30.140 --> 22:30.730
Okay?

22:31.220 --> 22:32.310
Thank you, Director Bai.

22:32.310 --> 22:33.030
Come on.

22:33.220 --> 22:35.100
Let's welcome Ms. Xu again

22:35.160 --> 22:36.820
with a warm round of applause.

22:48.600 --> 22:49.400
More passion!

22:51.610 --> 22:52.610
More enthusiasm!

23:00.230 --> 23:01.430
You went to the lobby?

23:01.750 --> 23:03.150
I just took a walk around.

23:11.220 --> 23:11.950
What's up?

23:12.620 --> 23:14.120
Isn't patrolling the lobby

23:14.120 --> 23:15.470
my daily routine?

23:15.500 --> 23:16.300
Is it strange?

23:16.510 --> 23:19.160
You patrolled exceptionally on time today.

23:20.060 --> 23:22.120
But it's right to make an appearance.

23:22.350 --> 23:24.410
Otherwise, a person like Xu Miyu

23:24.540 --> 23:26.720
falling into the hands of
those little girls,

23:26.720 --> 23:28.580
she would definitely be bullied.

23:28.710 --> 23:30.680
If she is really that inexperienced,

23:30.680 --> 23:32.680
it means our judgment is wrong.

23:33.280 --> 23:34.350
With real ability,

23:34.400 --> 23:36.200
one can stand firm anywhere.

23:37.370 --> 23:39.300
I can't win this argument with you.

23:39.720 --> 23:41.070
Who tried so hard

23:41.070 --> 23:42.750
to persuade others

23:42.750 --> 23:44.610
to give Xu Miyu this opportunity?

23:54.980 --> 23:55.770
[Memorandum of Understanding]

23:55.860 --> 23:56.640
[I'm from Jiang Zhichun's studio team.]

23:56.670 --> 23:57.390
[We're interested in the brand image and]

23:57.240 --> 23:58.510
Isn't this Dianjiangchun,

23:57.400 --> 23:57.910
[unique charm of Purong Hotel]

23:57.940 --> 23:58.440
[I think if we cooperate,
we will make great achievements.]

23:58.510 --> 24:00.790
who advertised for us last time?

24:03.440 --> 24:04.720
Such a popular blogger

24:04.720 --> 24:07.000
came to us many times.

24:07.240 --> 24:08.200
Could it be

24:08.200 --> 24:11.200
because of the grand opening of
the Chinese restaurant last time,

24:11.200 --> 24:12.930
or does she have other motives?

24:13.970 --> 24:14.960
No matter what,

24:15.240 --> 24:16.750
we have no reason

24:16.750 --> 24:18.750
to give up this opportunity, right?

24:23.160 --> 24:23.880
Okay.

24:24.240 --> 24:25.370
I'll think about it.

24:28.390 --> 24:30.190
[Purong Hotel Staff Apartment]

25:15.960 --> 25:18.550
That lobby manager just now
was so beautiful.

25:23.020 --> 25:24.820
Miyu looks really pretty today.

25:25.510 --> 25:27.170
Your girlfriend is watching.

25:29.960 --> 25:31.160
Hello, welcome.

25:31.160 --> 25:32.090
This way please.

25:37.680 --> 25:38.640
Excuse me.

25:38.640 --> 25:39.680
You dropped your scarf.

25:39.680 --> 25:40.360
Thank you.

25:40.440 --> 25:40.830
This way, please.

25:40.830 --> 25:41.490
Right here.

25:54.400 --> 25:55.340
Who is this?

25:55.400 --> 25:56.330
Hello, Mr. Duan.

25:57.330 --> 25:58.730
This is my former butler.

25:58.750 --> 25:59.950
Gorgeous, isn't she?

26:01.000 --> 26:03.310
I used to see you mopping floors
and cleaning toilets

26:03.310 --> 26:05.070
with your head down
in the executive lounge.

26:05.070 --> 26:07.530
I didn't expect you to be
such a great beauty.

26:07.550 --> 26:08.350
Thank you.

26:09.400 --> 26:10.400
It seems

26:10.400 --> 26:11.590
Ji Feng really has a good eye.

26:11.590 --> 26:12.880
Putting you in this position

26:12.880 --> 26:15.010
is making the best use of your talents.

26:15.750 --> 26:16.640
Let's go.

26:24.750 --> 26:25.440
Hello.

26:26.160 --> 26:27.960
Is there anything I can help you with?

26:27.960 --> 26:29.440
Excuse me, where is the sales department?

26:29.440 --> 26:31.250
You need to take the staff elevator
up to the third floor.

26:31.250 --> 26:32.070
Please follow me.

26:32.070 --> 26:33.000
Okay, thank you.

26:34.680 --> 26:36.440
I was just at the front of the line.

26:36.440 --> 26:38.750
I just went back to my suitcase
to get my ID card.

26:38.750 --> 26:40.350
Why do I have to line up again?

26:40.500 --> 26:41.620
That was just now.

26:41.920 --> 26:43.440
It took you too long to get your ID.

26:43.440 --> 26:44.640
We can't have so many people

26:44.640 --> 26:45.880
waiting just for you.

26:46.070 --> 26:48.160
How could you do this to me?

26:48.590 --> 26:49.000
You...

26:50.440 --> 26:51.370
Let me handle it.

26:52.310 --> 26:53.160
Hello, miss.

26:53.810 --> 26:55.010
I'm sorry about that.

26:55.070 --> 26:55.730
Lu Xiaoyan,

26:55.920 --> 26:57.640
please help this guest first.

26:57.750 --> 26:59.110
She was already here.

26:59.920 --> 27:01.590
If you miss your number,
you have to line up again.

27:01.590 --> 27:03.260
We all follow the rules

27:03.560 --> 27:04.740
fairly and justly.

27:06.920 --> 27:07.750
Ms. Xu.

27:08.480 --> 27:09.550
You don't know the reception work.

27:09.550 --> 27:11.160
So, could you please
stay out of this matter?

27:11.160 --> 27:12.160
I think you should

27:12.160 --> 27:14.090
take care of the guests over there.

27:17.400 --> 27:19.000
Do you have any tissues?

27:19.430 --> 27:20.360
Enjoy your stay.

27:24.050 --> 27:24.770
Thank you.

27:31.000 --> 27:33.000
Cleaners, please come to the lobby.

27:33.360 --> 27:34.040
Hello.

27:34.160 --> 27:36.080
She's your superior after all.

27:36.340 --> 27:37.820
Why make her do that?

27:40.350 --> 27:41.000
Come on.

27:41.000 --> 27:41.920
Take some tissues.

27:41.920 --> 27:42.400
Come on.

27:42.830 --> 27:44.560
Isn't that her old profession?

28:00.890 --> 28:01.960
You don't know the reception work.

28:01.960 --> 28:03.590
So, could you please
stay out of this matter?

28:03.590 --> 28:04.590
I think you should

28:04.590 --> 28:06.520
take care of the guests over there.

28:54.880 --> 28:55.750
Ms. Xu.

28:56.200 --> 28:57.000
Ms. Sun.

28:58.640 --> 28:59.640
It is you.

29:01.480 --> 29:03.160
You're getting prettier.

29:03.240 --> 29:04.680
I almost didn't recognize you.

29:04.680 --> 29:05.750
Ms. Sun, I'm sorry.

29:05.750 --> 29:07.310
I didn't have time to greet you.

29:07.310 --> 29:08.920
I'm transferred to the lobby now

29:08.920 --> 29:10.050
and become the lobby manager.

29:10.050 --> 29:11.440
Congratulations.

29:11.640 --> 29:12.750
Next time I come,

29:12.750 --> 29:13.750
can I see you in the lobby

29:13.750 --> 29:15.160
at a glance?

29:15.720 --> 29:18.000
Ms. Sun, maybe not.

29:18.200 --> 29:19.000
Why?

29:19.400 --> 29:21.400
With Ms. Xu's promotion speed,

29:21.420 --> 29:23.130
now she is the lobby manager,

29:23.200 --> 29:24.160
but next time you come here,

29:24.160 --> 29:26.760
she might be
the assistant of general manager.

29:27.480 --> 29:29.200
Thank you for flattering me, Ms. Lu.

29:29.200 --> 29:30.310
I will definitely work hard

29:30.310 --> 29:31.570
and won't let you down.

29:32.240 --> 29:34.070
I like your personality.

29:34.110 --> 29:35.510
You are brave and driven.

29:36.200 --> 29:36.830
Keep it up.

29:37.400 --> 29:38.400
I'll leave first.

29:38.440 --> 29:38.920
Thank you.

29:38.920 --> 29:39.350
Bye.

29:39.550 --> 29:40.350
Take care, Ms. Sun.

29:40.350 --> 29:41.400
Ms. Sun, this way.

29:52.310 --> 29:53.240
No.

29:53.400 --> 29:55.260
I want you to pick me up after work.

29:55.750 --> 29:57.200
I don't want to eat at home.

29:57.200 --> 29:59.400
I have something important to tell you.

30:00.640 --> 30:01.440
The baby is fine.

30:01.440 --> 30:02.750
The baby is okay.

30:06.000 --> 30:07.400
Ms. Lu, please sign here.

30:07.680 --> 30:08.690
I don't care.

30:09.240 --> 30:12.000
I want you to get off work early today
and pick me up.

30:12.000 --> 30:12.920
At 5 o'clock.

30:16.310 --> 30:17.240
Love you, honey.

30:18.230 --> 30:19.040
See you later.

30:29.720 --> 30:30.350
Miss.

30:30.730 --> 30:31.200
Hello.

30:31.200 --> 30:32.960
We want to try yellow-feathered chicken.

30:32.960 --> 30:35.640
Do you know which restaurant nearby
is the best?

30:35.640 --> 30:37.000
You want to eat yellow-feathered chicken?

30:37.000 --> 30:38.510
There are a few
good restaurants around here.

30:38.510 --> 30:39.510
Please follow me.

30:39.650 --> 30:40.280
Okay.

30:43.640 --> 30:44.720
This way, please.

30:46.740 --> 30:47.570
Look.

30:47.590 --> 30:49.960
Go out this exit and turn right.

30:50.110 --> 30:51.110
Then at the intersection over there,

30:51.110 --> 30:51.970
turn left.

30:52.030 --> 30:55.030
You will see a restaurant
after walking about 100 meters.

30:55.030 --> 30:55.960
Thank you, miss.

30:55.960 --> 30:56.890
You're welcome.

30:56.920 --> 30:57.590
Take care.

30:58.200 --> 30:58.960
Honey.

31:14.290 --> 31:15.550
Who are you looking at?

31:15.680 --> 31:16.550
Nothing.

31:17.010 --> 31:19.010
Just waiting for you to get off work.

31:22.880 --> 31:23.640
Drive.

31:34.880 --> 31:37.170
This is the first Mediterranean restaurant

31:37.170 --> 31:39.750
opened in China by Laura Garcia,

31:39.750 --> 31:41.270
the famous Spanish chef.

31:42.680 --> 31:43.550
Here,

31:43.670 --> 31:46.240
you can taste
the most authentic Mediterranean food

31:46.240 --> 31:48.510
in a strong artistic atmosphere.

31:49.200 --> 31:50.510
In Shanghai's spring,

31:50.750 --> 31:53.510
this is a good choice
to gather with friends.

31:57.510 --> 31:58.710
My old friend is here.

31:59.800 --> 32:00.510
Have a seat.

32:00.510 --> 32:01.240
Okay.

32:03.590 --> 32:04.350
I knew

32:04.960 --> 32:06.270
you'd only come to see me

32:06.270 --> 32:07.600
under the guise of work.

32:17.350 --> 32:18.640
On our opening day,

32:19.140 --> 32:21.580
I didn't know you were there.

32:22.830 --> 32:24.230
Have I changed that much?

32:24.350 --> 32:26.210
I recognized you at first glance.

32:26.960 --> 32:28.960
It was mainly because
there were too many people that day.

32:28.960 --> 32:30.510
Because of your video,

32:31.030 --> 32:32.270
many customers

32:32.470 --> 32:33.590
came to our restaurant.

32:33.590 --> 32:35.060
Good wine needs no bush.

32:35.090 --> 32:36.590
Your new signature dishes are

32:36.590 --> 32:38.160
truly amazing.

32:40.790 --> 32:42.390
When did you return to China?

32:43.270 --> 32:44.830
Last November.

32:45.590 --> 32:47.000
You spent ten years abroad before.

32:47.000 --> 32:47.960
As soon as you came back,

32:47.960 --> 32:50.690
you took over such a hot potato
like Purong Hotel.

32:50.920 --> 32:52.850
I mainly wanted to save this place,

32:53.480 --> 32:54.240
and also give my career

32:54.240 --> 32:55.680
a happy ending.

32:56.270 --> 32:57.400
You are indeed loyal and righteous.

32:57.400 --> 32:58.350
Not exactly.

32:59.240 --> 33:00.570
Just acting on impulse.

33:06.620 --> 33:07.620
It's been a while.

33:07.670 --> 33:09.850
Aren't you going to ask me how I've been?

33:09.850 --> 33:11.680
I don't think I have to ask.

33:12.090 --> 33:13.830
You are the head of Dianjiangchun team,

33:13.830 --> 33:16.960
an influencer brand
with tens of millions of followers.

33:17.700 --> 33:20.180
Although I've achieved my small dream

33:20.310 --> 33:21.510
and earned money,

33:21.720 --> 33:24.750
I'm still alone.

33:25.410 --> 33:26.270
What about you,

33:26.480 --> 33:27.360
Mr. Ji?

33:27.390 --> 33:28.920
Are you as miserable as I am?

33:29.350 --> 33:30.950
Don't think too highly of me.

33:31.270 --> 33:32.510
I'm still the same.

33:32.590 --> 33:33.270
Then,

33:33.680 --> 33:35.280
we're in the same situation.

33:41.350 --> 33:44.400
So, how exactly does Ms. Jiang want to

33:44.850 --> 33:47.610
cooperate with Purong Hotel?

33:49.270 --> 33:51.260
The famous Purong Hotel in Shanghai

33:51.260 --> 33:53.320
actually has many themes to explore.

33:54.000 --> 33:56.000
It depends on how far Mr. Ji

33:56.020 --> 33:57.780
wants to go with me.

33:57.830 --> 33:59.170
For a win-win cooperation,

33:59.170 --> 34:00.680
I will hold nothing back, of course.

34:00.680 --> 34:01.550
Don't worry.

34:01.960 --> 34:03.690
I'll fully cooperate with you.

34:04.790 --> 34:05.790
Let's eat and talk.

34:05.790 --> 34:07.160
The food here is delicious.

34:07.160 --> 34:07.830
Give it a try.

34:07.830 --> 34:08.670
Let's try it.

34:30.760 --> 34:31.570
What's up, baby?

34:31.570 --> 34:32.969
I don't have an appetite.

34:35.030 --> 34:36.489
Is the baby bothering you?

34:37.320 --> 34:38.550
I wonder who it was

34:38.550 --> 34:40.179
staring at his ex-wife

34:40.210 --> 34:42.800
at the entrance of Purong Hotel today?

34:43.389 --> 34:44.270
What?

34:44.290 --> 34:45.480
Now that she's promoted to

34:45.480 --> 34:46.730
lobby manager,

34:46.760 --> 34:48.050
you're tempted again, aren't you?

34:48.050 --> 34:48.900
No, I'm not.

34:50.090 --> 34:50.699
I mean,

34:51.560 --> 34:52.730
you and the baby are

34:52.760 --> 34:54.280
the only things in my world now.

34:54.280 --> 34:55.320
I wouldn't think of anything else.

34:55.320 --> 34:56.719
Spare me your sweet talk.

34:57.020 --> 34:58.620
I'm involved in

34:58.640 --> 34:59.480
your history of cheating, okay?

34:59.480 --> 35:01.280
It's not fair for you to say that.

35:01.280 --> 35:02.570
When have I ever lied to you?

35:02.570 --> 35:03.440
Nie Yucheng, your acting like this

35:03.440 --> 35:04.840
makes me very insecure.

35:06.320 --> 35:08.360
Okay, let me tell you some good news

35:08.360 --> 35:10.020
to put your mind at ease, okay?

35:11.960 --> 35:14.320
What good news could you possibly have?
Let's hear it.

35:14.320 --> 35:16.180
I was promoted to vice president.

35:19.510 --> 35:22.920
Shouldn't you have been promoted

35:24.280 --> 35:25.920
to vice president a long time ago?

35:25.920 --> 35:27.800
Does that not satisfy you either?

35:27.820 --> 35:28.930
Okay then, tell me.

35:28.960 --> 35:30.330
Let me know what you want

35:30.350 --> 35:31.660
so I can satisfy you.

35:35.710 --> 35:38.240
Sign the contract for the new house
next week.

35:41.360 --> 35:42.360
Well, as for this...

35:42.360 --> 35:44.210
Didn't you say there was no rush before?

35:44.210 --> 35:45.410
How is this not a rush?

35:46.480 --> 35:47.960
Look how big my belly is.

35:48.280 --> 35:49.280
I'm going to give birth soon.

35:49.280 --> 35:50.630
Where will the child live when it's born?

35:50.630 --> 35:52.800
The three of us live in one room
with your mom?

35:52.800 --> 35:54.000
Is that appropriate?

35:55.920 --> 35:56.920
Okay. Fine.

35:56.920 --> 35:58.120
But the problem is that

35:58.120 --> 35:59.400
our family doesn't have

35:59.400 --> 36:00.840
that much spare money.

36:00.840 --> 36:01.880
We do.

36:01.880 --> 36:04.280
Where did your millions in investments go?

36:04.960 --> 36:07.710
I don't think we should use that money.

36:08.670 --> 36:10.590
Nie Yucheng, what do you mean?

36:10.590 --> 36:12.280
Why are you always making excuses?

36:12.280 --> 36:13.230
Do you not love me and the baby?

36:13.230 --> 36:13.670
No, no, no.

36:13.670 --> 36:14.360
Tell the truth.

36:14.360 --> 36:14.760
No.

36:14.920 --> 36:17.320
Don't blow it out of proportion.
I love you.

36:22.190 --> 36:22.960
Fine.

36:23.400 --> 36:24.480
I promise you then.

36:25.480 --> 36:26.070
Really?

36:26.280 --> 36:26.880
Really.

36:27.480 --> 36:28.410
I guarantee that

36:28.480 --> 36:31.070
the baby will live in a new house
upon birth.

36:32.800 --> 36:33.710
Are you lying?

36:33.710 --> 36:34.760
I'm not lying.

36:34.760 --> 36:36.290
When have I ever lied to you?

36:37.800 --> 36:38.630
Are you happy?

36:39.880 --> 36:41.280
You're happy now.

36:42.070 --> 36:42.960
Okay, okay, okay.

36:42.960 --> 36:44.290
As long as you're happy.

36:48.810 --> 36:50.270
It must have been ten years

36:50.270 --> 36:51.620
since last time

36:52.010 --> 36:54.210
we walked side by side like this, right?

36:54.770 --> 36:55.920
Time flies.

36:58.030 --> 36:58.800
You know,

36:59.600 --> 37:01.040
over the past ten years,

37:01.510 --> 37:03.310
I've been having the same dream.

37:04.660 --> 37:06.660
I dreamed of the day I left the house,

37:07.130 --> 37:08.630
dragging my luggage.

37:12.920 --> 37:13.710
Back then,

37:14.530 --> 37:16.790
I always wanted to see the results first.

37:18.400 --> 37:19.400
I was so impatient

37:19.920 --> 37:20.670
and anxious.

37:23.160 --> 37:25.840
And I left you so easily.

37:30.030 --> 37:30.550
Ji Feng.

37:34.600 --> 37:35.410
I'm sorry.

37:37.170 --> 37:38.770
You don't have to apologize.

37:40.080 --> 37:41.680
We were both young back then.

37:41.880 --> 37:43.480
I was just a hotel attendant.

37:44.400 --> 37:46.260
I couldn't even see my own future,

37:46.710 --> 37:48.800
let alone give you the life you wanted.

37:48.800 --> 37:50.770
It was right for you to leave.

37:50.790 --> 37:52.050
At least after leaving me,

37:52.050 --> 37:53.780
you did what you wanted to do,

37:54.150 --> 37:55.880
experienced a wider world,

37:56.430 --> 37:58.030
and became who you are today.

37:59.070 --> 38:00.730
So you don't blame me anymore?

38:05.000 --> 38:06.130
It's all in the past.

38:07.920 --> 38:08.550
Really.

38:08.700 --> 38:10.630
Seeing how successful you are now,

38:11.110 --> 38:12.280
I'm very happy for you.

38:12.280 --> 38:13.000
Me too.

38:14.190 --> 38:16.850
You're still the same as
I knew you ten years ago.

38:17.590 --> 38:18.320
That's nice.

38:23.800 --> 38:26.760
Here's to a pleasant cooperation ahead.

38:27.320 --> 38:28.920
Yes, to a great cooperation.

38:45.440 --> 38:48.000
I wish all the musicians

38:48.000 --> 38:49.760
a successful performance tonight.

38:49.760 --> 38:50.670
Just wait for

38:50.700 --> 38:52.150
a big surprise.

38:55.190 --> 38:56.500
Should we play a piece

38:56.630 --> 38:57.920
for Miyu

38:57.920 --> 38:58.760
to reward her?

38:58.760 --> 38:59.320
Let's play one piece for her.

38:59.320 --> 38:59.880
Okay.

38:59.880 --> 39:00.480
Here we go.

39:36.670 --> 39:38.420
Hello, Mr. Ji and Mr. Xue.

39:39.590 --> 39:41.840
I just came to remind everyone

39:41.840 --> 39:43.360
that tonight's performance

39:43.360 --> 39:44.760
will last for a long time.

39:44.760 --> 39:46.530
Take the time to rest for a while.

39:46.530 --> 39:47.570
No problem.

39:49.670 --> 39:52.470
I'll leave the Western restaurant to you
tonight.

40:01.770 --> 40:02.870
Be careful, guys.

40:03.510 --> 40:04.970
A little lower over there.

40:07.630 --> 40:08.320
How is it?

40:08.320 --> 40:10.510
How do you feel after listening to it?

40:11.360 --> 40:12.880
You really dare to think and act,

40:12.880 --> 40:15.010
getting a group of seniors to perform.

40:16.590 --> 40:19.280
I admire your courage.

40:19.960 --> 40:21.190
Rui, are you being sarcastic?

40:21.190 --> 40:21.840
No.

40:21.960 --> 40:23.400
They played very well.

40:23.400 --> 40:24.980
I was also shocked just now.

40:25.030 --> 40:26.110
With a performance of this level,

40:26.110 --> 40:28.760
the alumni association
will definitely be thrilled tonight.

40:28.760 --> 40:30.260
It will give everyone a pleasant surprise.

40:30.260 --> 40:31.360
Pleasant is fine,

40:31.360 --> 40:32.710
but surprise is unnecessary.

40:32.710 --> 40:34.320
After all, they are old.

40:34.520 --> 40:37.650
We still need to be careful
with tonight's performance.

40:37.680 --> 40:39.670
Have the logistics team
keep a close eye on things,

40:39.670 --> 40:41.480
and prepare various contingency plans
just in case.

40:41.480 --> 40:43.000
Okay, I'll go check.

40:43.000 --> 40:43.630
Okay.

40:57.670 --> 40:59.260
[Purong Hotel]

41:04.590 --> 41:06.400
Why does she keep running

41:06.400 --> 41:08.030
to the Western restaurant today?

41:08.030 --> 41:09.110
That goes without saying.

41:09.110 --> 41:10.240
She went to show off.

41:11.800 --> 41:13.840
There's a performance
at the Western restaurant tonight.

41:13.840 --> 41:15.370
She got transferred there.

41:16.840 --> 41:17.840
Alright.

41:18.110 --> 41:19.670
She's just a cleaner from
the HSKP Department.

41:19.670 --> 41:20.880
What's there to envy?

41:21.000 --> 41:22.190
Stop talking about her all day

41:22.190 --> 41:23.390
and making her a star.

41:26.520 --> 41:32.350
[60th Anniversary of
Lussia University Alumni Association]

41:44.960 --> 41:45.840
Ming.

41:46.250 --> 41:47.520
Eat slowly.

41:47.670 --> 41:48.480
Don't eat too much.

41:48.480 --> 41:50.150
You have a performance tonight.

41:50.150 --> 41:51.880
A full stomach gives me energy.

41:59.320 --> 42:00.840
See, what did I tell you?

42:03.920 --> 42:04.710
Ming.

42:05.600 --> 42:06.640
What's wrong?

42:10.190 --> 42:11.070
How is it?

42:13.150 --> 42:14.110
It's stuck.

42:14.110 --> 42:14.670
Is it?

42:14.670 --> 42:15.590
What's wrong? What's wrong?

42:15.590 --> 42:16.840
M-Maybe it's stuck?

42:16.840 --> 42:17.770
Choking on food.
